      - Koide ratio 2/3? (a rational from a quantization condition?)

  The KEY INSIGHT for Phase 4:
    The PSLQ null tested LINEAR combinations.
    The synthesis says: look for MODULAR relationships with
    modulus 8R₂ (for phase parameters) or modulus 1 (for topological).
    These are different operations — the null on linear search
    does not constrain the modular search.

